        {
          "attributes":
          {
            "documentation": "@notice Token owner can approve for `spender` to transferFrom(...) `tokens` from the token owner's account. The `spender` contract function `receiveApproval(...)` is then executed\n @dev Token owner can approve for `spender` to transferFrom(...) `tokens` from the token owner's account. The `spender` contract function `receiveApproval(...)` is then executed\n @param spender The contract address to be approved\n @param tokens The number of tokens the caller is approving for `spender` to use\n @param data The function call data provided to `spender.receiveApproval()`",
